{"tid":1515807,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元軍控制嚴密，義軍無法傳遞消息，在中秋節互贈的月餅裡面夾紙條。","createTime":"2019-08-29T10:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T13:54:11.000Z","uid":227801,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ca6d0013d608d6aac69e520be94110be7c73fc","tid":1515807,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:17:04.000Z","msg":"八月十五殺韃子，是在中國廣為流傳的一個故事。<br />\n元朝末年，廣大中原人民不堪元政府的殘暴統治，朱元璋揭竿反元，但元軍控制嚴密，義軍無法傳遞消息，適逢中秋節將至，劉伯溫獻計，在中秋節互贈的月餅裡面夾紙條，上面寫著「八月十五殺韃子」。<br />\n<br />\n故事起源和傳播編輯<br />\n<br />\n此事之時、地未見於各史冊記載，僅止於傳說故事。故事的雛形見於清朝光緒首次刊行的元初徐大焯《燼餘錄》，該故事是描繪蒙古兵進入蘇州吳縣後對當地的殘虐。後來有人摘採《元史》及蒙古族相傳元朝虐政的記載加以改編，當劉伯溫作策劃月餅傳訊的主謀，合成完整的「八月十五殺韃子」傳奇故事。<br />\n此故事結合劉伯溫《燒餅歌》讖言預測滿清滅亡的傳說，以蒙元影射滿清，配合「驅除韃虜、恢復中華」的漢民族革命的宣傳，於清末至民初的反清排滿浪潮中迅速傳播。變為家傳戶誦的中秋民間傳說，直至現在。辛亥革命時，在陝西，八月十五殺韃子成為革命黨鼓動革命的口號。革命黨在各城張貼標語，鼓動造反，民間大量流傳八月十五殺韃子的說法。"},{"pid":"54bf8b4eeb973a797b072c8f795bb35860655702","tid":1515807,"uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"月餅初心的故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168bfb59461f6b767ac84d2d8ca6c4004f7e2a60","tid":1515807,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e509598c100de69b9578c7e2ee4ad5b12dfc7ab","tid":1515807,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e84726ea47e7a570beac0002bf87fd11945bbb","tid":1515807,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1683ccce414da2ff5863d64225b14616713c12","tid":1515807,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果每個人都post張有字條既月餅會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cb7c82d59f291d70b0b6ffabe267dd46395fca","tid":1515807,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41830189afc9886ba120415068ec8989f12353a","tid":1515807,"uid":155789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傳到去共產黨未"},{"pid":"07cc287a33ba7c83039d008fe8a916a529058d3f","tid":1515807,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}